  <h2 id="meal-plan">3-Day High-Protein Meal Plan</h2>
  <p>This sample plan targets approximately 130–140 g of protein and 1,500–1,600 kcal per day — suitable for a 70–80 kg person aiming to lose fat. Adjust portions up or down based on your calorie target from our <a href="calorie-calculator.html">Calorie Calculator</a>.</p>

  <h3>Day 1</h3>
  <div class="card" style="padding:16px 20px;margin:12px 0;border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:10px;">
    <p><strong>Breakfast:</strong> 3 scrambled eggs + 150g Greek yoghurt + 1 banana → ~42g protein, ~420 kcal</p>
    <p><strong>Lunch:</strong> 150g chicken breast + 150g brown rice + large green salad with olive oil dressing → ~47g protein, ~520 kcal</p>
    <p><strong>Snack:</strong> 150g cottage cheese + cucumber → ~18g protein, ~130 kcal</p>
    <p><strong>Dinner:</strong> 150g salmon + 200g roasted vegetables + 100g quinoa → ~38g protein, ~530 kcal</p>
    <p style="color:var(--ink3);font-size:.85rem;margin:0;"><strong>Total: ~145g protein · ~1,600 kcal</strong></p>
  </div>

